Question: What will be the output when the following code fragment is run?
int x = 12, y = 14, z;
z = y / x +7;
x = z * z;
System.Console.WriteLine(x);
Answer Options:
0 (Incorrect)
12 (Incorrect)
64 (Correct)
none of the above (Incorrect)
