Question: static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            string str = "Hello";
            ChangeString(str);
            Console.WriteLine(str);
}
        static void ChangeString(string str)
        {
            str += "Hi";
}
Answer Options:
Hello (Correct)
Hi (Incorrect)
HelloHi (Incorrect)
It does not compile. (Incorrect)
